Package com.ait_31_2.doctor_appointment_app.domain.dto

Class AppointmentDto

java.lang.Object
com.ait_31_2.doctor_appointment_app.domain.dto.AppointmentDto
public class AppointmentDto extends Object
DTO class representing an appointment. Contains information about the appointment, including ID, patient ID, doctor ID, slot ID, date, and visit completion status.
